   Western District of Washington U.S.B.C.Court Forms

   Subject:   Last Updated: Comments:
   Claim Form 08/15/2001    Revised 4/1/01

   Automatic adjustments to the dollar amounts in various provisions of
   the Bankruptcy Code are effective April 1, 2001. Specific changes to
   the Proof of Claim Form are limited to section 6, Unsecured Priority
   Claim. The increased dollar amounts apply to cases filed April 1, 2001
   or later. They are as follows:

   -- Wages, Salaries or Commissions: Claim limit increased to $4,650
   (Note: amount is $4,000 for cases filed prior to 4/1/98, and $4,300 for
   cases filed prior to 4/1/01).

   -- Deposits toward purchase, lease, or rental of property of the
   estate: Claim limit increased to $2,100 (Note: amount is $1,800 for
   cases filed prior to 4/1/98, and $1,950 for cases filed prior to
   4/1/01).

   You may download the forms as Word Perfect or Adobe Portable Document
   Format.. Claim4-01seattle.pdf contains the address of the Seattle
   Clerk's Office. The Claim4-01tacoma.pdf contains the Tacoma address.
   Click on the appropriate icon to begin your download.

